{"tid":2367472,"cid":21,"subCid":4,"title":"[BLINK] BLACKPINK討論區(9) 0116 PricelessJennieDay!!","createTime":"2021-01-15T11:14:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T11:14:16.000Z","uid":32551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"365efaa7b39aa49090b5ca4a1a60f34f7390b654","tid":2367472,"uid":32551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:14:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ErujcNeVgAABGze?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FErujcNeVgAABGze%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dorig&h=cc3f0bb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://assets2.rappler.com/2020/12/20201203-BLACKPINK-the-show-1606973158629.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets2.rappler.com%2F2020%2F12%2F20201203-BLACKPINK-the-show-1606973158629.jpeg&h=15c37e46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"pink\">BLACKPINK</span></strong>（韓語：블랙핑크）是YG娛樂於2016年推出的韓國女子音樂組合，由JISOO、JENNIE、ROS&Eacute;與LISA四名成員組成。2016年8月8日以數碼專輯《SQUARE ONE》正式出道。<br />\n<br />\nYG娛樂表示BLACK PINK帶有稍微否定粉紅色是最美的顏色的涵義，具有「漂亮並不代表全部」的反轉意義，也表示成員們不僅具備外貌、同時也兼具實力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CpVnIctUEAEN8Jj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCpVnIctUEAEN8Jj.jpg&h=99f96d7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一張數碼專輯《SQUARE ONE》<br />\n發行日期：2016年8月8日<br />\n主打曲:<br />\n1. 휘파람（WHISTLE）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dISNgvVpWlo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdISNgvVpWlo&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=5a6c5bc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dISNgvVpWlo</a><br />\n2.붐바야（BOOMBAYAH）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bwmSjveL3Lc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbwmSjveL3Lc&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=dc0fd185\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bwmSjveL3Lc</a><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CxQArD7WgAACk_H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCxQArD7WgAACk_H.jpg&h=fcd89d7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二張數碼專輯《SQUARE TWO》<br />\n發行日期：2016年11月1日<br />\n主打曲<br />\n1.불장난（PLAYING WITH FIRE）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9pdj4iJD08s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9pdj4iJD08s&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=eb458d32\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9pdj4iJD08s</a><br />\n2.STAY<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FzVR_fymZw4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFzVR_fymZw4&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=dc141ae0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FzVR_fymZw4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DC6n1aOU0AA5-EN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDC6n1aOU0AA5-EN.jpg&h=061b0819&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一張數碼單曲《마지막처럼》AS IF IT'S YOUR LAST<br />\n發行日期：2017年6月22日<br />\n主打曲<br />\n1. 마지막처럼（AS IF IT'S YOUR LAST）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Amq-qlqbjYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAmq-qlqbjYA&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=638353c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Amq-qlqbjYA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.imageimg.net/artist/blackpink/img/product_1025827.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.imageimg.net%2Fartist%2Fblackpink%2Fimg%2Fproduct_1025827.jpg&h=ab9b832f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJAPAN DEBUT MINI ALBUM『BLACKPINK』<br />\n發行日期：2017年8月30日<br />\nCD ONLY<br />\n01 BOOMBAYAH  <br />\n02 WHISTLE  <br />\n03 